{"tid":1987980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社︰中国官員率領醫療專家急赴北韓","createTime":"2020-04-25T01:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T02:26:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"af9e4e134d1a36498adec19e5c4b7b550cb22ca4","tid":1987980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:07:30.000Z","msg":"路透社引述消息人士報道，中國向北韓派出一支包括醫療專家的團隊，但未知是否與北韓領袖金正恩的健康情況有關。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中共中央對外聯絡部一名高級官員，星期四率領團隊在北京出發，前往北韓，中國外交部暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒早前傳出，金正恩接受手術後情況危急，但美國總統特朗普其後表示，金正恩病危的報道不正確。路透社早前引述南韓一名消息人士指，金正恩仍然在生，可能很快會露面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522652-20200425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522652-20200425.htm&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=e0669e1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522652-20200425.htm&h=f020adeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522652-20200425.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d839af79da78cd81fa0251dc65ca136b7c2f510e","tid":1987980,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WO0Fp6MU8u4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWO0Fp6MU8u4&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=a7215cd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WO0Fp6MU8u4</a>"},{"pid":"85ba6c3fc082b95097461c52a70e4076f7af905c","tid":1987980,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"中國醫療專家？<br />\nCPR都唔識做嗰啲？"},{"pid":"aaf9432a845a3297010ff649f0421b476db8134c","tid":1987980,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85ba6c3fc082b95097461c52a70e4076f7af905c","tid":1987980,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:16:27.000Z",